<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>Ferrum College offers advanced standing to those students who satisfactorily demonstrate a high level of proficiency in a given subject area. Course credit, as well as advanced standing, may be earned through the Advanced Placement Program of the College Entrance Examination Board. Advanced Placement Credit may be granted upon presentation of a score of 3 or above.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.ferrum.edu/academics/registrars_office/advanced_placement_equivalency_guide.aspx" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
</p>

